    <h1 id="maincontent">Get Involved!<em style="font-size:16px; color:#999; text-shadow:none;"> - &ldquo;The  End of Bullying Begins With You&rdquo; </em></h1>
<table><tr>
<td valign="top" width="60%"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td width="99%" valign="top"><p>Bullying touches so many lives. It often inspires the generous spirit in people who want to make a difference, support the cause, and change something that has happened to too many for too long. Every day, students, parents, schools, and community members ask us, &ldquo;What can I do to help?&rdquo; Every contribution &mdash; whether it&rsquo;s hosting a community event, standing up for someone, or giving a donation to an organization that addresses bullying &mdash; makes a difference and changes lives.</p>
